		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I learned from NES 101 and as many other docs I could get my hands on at the time (including nestech).  This was before Bunnyboy's Nerdy Nights which is now probably the best tutorial for newcomers.
<br />
<br />As others have said, don't use GBAGuy's tutorials.  The reason you can't get his code to work is because it's wrong.

		

